  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Prospective-randomized trial. Patients with recurrent bleeding from gastroduodenal ulcers are
      randomized into either endoscopic treatment with the OTSC [Over The Scope Clip] or endoscopic
      standard therapy. Hypothesis: Endoscopic therapy with OTSC is superior to standard therapy
      regarding technical success and rebleeding.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
